boulevard saintlaurent  saint laurent boulevard  known locally as the main or saint lawrence boulevard is one of the best places to find nightlife with many bars and nightclubs and a wide range of restaurants saintlaurent street night spots are often less mainstream than those on crescent street with a great variety from top 40 and urban music to electronica and techno from underground and alternative rock to live bands south of prince arthur street toward  sherbrooke street  one is likely to encounter a posher clientele from prince arthur street north to avenue montroyal and beyond one should expect to rub shoulders with an edgier crowd the nearest subway stops are  saintlaurent  and  sherbrooke
